<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="gu">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>🌾 ખેડૂત પોર્ટલ - Complete</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #87CEEB 0%, #d4af37 40%, #8B7355 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2ecc71 0%, #27ae60 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.2em;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .nav-tabs {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .nav-btn {
            background: white;
            color: #2ecc71;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .nav-btn.active {
            background: #2ecc71;
            color: white;
        }

        .content-section {
            display: none;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .content-section.active {
            display: block;
        }

        .section-title {
            color: #2ecc71;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #2ecc71;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #333;
        }

        input, select, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 1em;
        }

        input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #2ecc71;
        }

        .btn-submit {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2ecc71 0%, #27ae60 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .success-msg {
            background: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: none;
        }

        .contact-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f6f9fc 0%, #e9f2f9 100%);
            border: 2px solid #2ecc71;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: #2ecc71;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .info {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #2ecc71;
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .delete-btn {
            background: #e74c3c;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .empty {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #999;
        }

        .two-col {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .news-item {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #2ecc71;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .news-title {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .price-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .price-table th {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2ecc71 0%, #27ae60 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .price-table td {
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .price-table tr:hover {
            background: #f1f8f4;
        }

        .weather-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #56CCF2 0%, #2F80ED 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .scheme-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .scheme-card h4 {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .two-col {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .nav-btn {
                padding: 8px 15px;
                font-size: 0.9em;
            }
        }

        /* LOGIN STYLES */
        .login-container {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #87CEEB 0%, #d4af37 40%, #8B7355 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 9999;
        }

        .login-box {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            padding: 40px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
        }

        .login-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .login-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #2ecc71;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .login-header p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .login-form {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .login-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .login-group label {
            display: block;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .login-group input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1em;
        }

        .login-group input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #2ecc71;
        }

        .login-btn {
            width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2ecc71 0%, #27ae60 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .login-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.4);
        }

        .error-msg {
            background: #f8d7da;
            color: #721c24;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: none;
        }

        .success-msg {
            background: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: none;
        }

        .signup-link {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .signup-link a {
            color: #2ecc71;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .signup-link a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .logout-btn {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            background: #e74c3c;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            display: none;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logout-btn:hover {
            background: #c0392b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- LOGIN PAGE -->
    <div id="loginPage" class="login-container">
        <div class="login-box">
            <div class="login-header">
                <h1>🌾 ખેડૂત પોર્ટલ</h1>
                <p>ખેડૂત અને મજુરો માટે સોલ્યુશન</p>
            </div>

            <div id="loginError" class="error-msg"></div>
            <div id="signupSuccess" class="success-msg"></div>

            <!-- Login Form -->
            <div id="loginForm">
                <h2 style="color: #2ecc71; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">🔐 Login</h2>
                <form id="userLogin" class="login-form">
                    <div class="login-group">
                        <label>Username:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="loginUsername" placeholder="તમારું Username" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="login-group">
                        <label>Password:</label>
                        <input type="password" id="loginPassword" placeholder="તમારું Password" required>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="login-btn">🔓 Login</button>
                </form>

                <div class="signup-link">
                    નવો user છો? 
                    <a onclick="toggleSignup()">અહીં Register કરો</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Signup Form -->
            <div id="signupForm" style="display: none;">
                <h2 style="color: #2ecc71; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">✍️ નવો Account બનાવો</h2>
                <form id="userSignup" class="login-form">
                    <div class="login-group">
                        <label>Username:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="signupUsername" placeholder="Username બનાવો" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="login-group">
                        <label>Password:</label>
                        <input type="password" id="signupPassword" placeholder="Password બનાવો" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="login-group">
                        <label>Password Confirm:</label>
                        <input type="password" id="confirmPassword" placeholder="Password ફરી લખો" required>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="login-btn">✅ Register</button>
                </form>

                <div class="signup-link">
                    પહલેથી Account છે? 
                    <a onclick="toggleSignup()">અહીં Login કરો</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <button class="logout-btn" onclick="logout()">🚪 Logout</button>

    <!-- MAIN WEBSITE -->
    <div id="mainContent">
        <header>
            <h1>🌾 ખેડૂત પોર્ટલ Gujarat</h1>
            <p>ખેડૂત અને મજુરો માટે સંપૂર્ણ સોલ્યુશન</p>
        </header>

        <div class="nav-tabs">
            <button class="nav-btn active" onclick="showSection('weather')">🌦️ હવામાન</button>
            <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('schemes')">🏛️ યોજના</button>
            <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('budget')">💰 બજટ</button>
            <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('contact')">🤝 સંપર્ક</button>
            <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('market')">🛒 માર્કેટ</button>
            <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('news')">📰 સમાચાર</button>
            <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('shops')">🏪 દુકાન</button>
            <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('prices')">💵 ભાવ</button>
        </div>

        <!-- 1. WEATHER SECTION -->
        <div id="weather" class="content-section active">
            <h2 class="section-title">🌦️ લાઇવ હવામાન અને મોન્સુન</h2>
            
            <!-- MONSOON TRACKER -->
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db 0%, #2980b9 100%); color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 15px;">🌧️ લાઇવ મોન્સુન ટ્રેકર 2026</h3>
                
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;">
                        <div style="font-size: 0.9em; opacity: 0.9;">કુલ વરસાદ (2026)</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0;">847 mm</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 0.9em;">Normal: 734 mm</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;">
                        <div style="font-size: 0.9em; opacity: 0.9;">પ્રગતિ</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0;">73%</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 0.9em;">Jun-Sep માર્જિન</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;">
                        <div style="font-size: 0.9em; opacity: 0.9;">આજનો વરસાદ</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0;">64 mm</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 0.9em;">આજ સુધી</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Progress Bar -->
                <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 3px; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    <div style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2ecc71 0%, #27ae60 100%); width: 73%; padding: 8px; text-align: center; color: white; font-weight: bold;">73% ✓</div>
                </div>

                <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    <strong>📊 Status:</strong> વરસાદ Normal થી 23% વધુ છે ✓
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- WEATHER BY LOCATION -->
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #56CCF2 0%, #2F80ED 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <h3 style="margin-bottom: 15px;">📍 તમારું સ્થળ પસંદ કરો</h3>
                <select id="weatherLocation" onchange="updateWeather()" style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px; width: 100%; border: none;">
                    <option value="surat">સુરત</option>
                    <option value="ahmedabad">અમદાવાદ</option>
                    <option value="rajkot">રાજકોટ</option>
                    <option value="vadodara">વડોદરા</option>
                    <option value="bhavnagar">ભાવનગર</option>
                    <option value="jamnagar">જામનગર</option>
                    <option value="anand">આણંદ</option>
                </select>
                <div style="font-size: 3em; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;" id="tempDisplay">32°C</div>
                <div style="font-size: 1.1em;">
                    <div id="weatherDesc">☁️ વાદળછાયું</div>
                    <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                        <span id="humidityDisplay">💧 ભેજ: 68%</span> | 
                        <span id="windDisplay">💨 પવન: 15 km/h</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- MONSOON FORECAST -->
            <div style="background: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #3498db;">
                <h3 style="color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 15px;">📅 આવતા 7 દિવસનો વરસાદ આગાહી</h3>
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr); gap: 10px;">
                    <div style="background: #ecf0f1; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
                        <div style="font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 8px;">સોમ</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 1.5em;">☁️</div>
                        <div style="color: #3498db; font-weight: bold; margin: 8px 0;">24mm</div>
                        <div style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9em;">65%</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: #ecf0f1; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
                        <div style="font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 8px;">મંગળ</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 1.5em;">🌧️</div>
                        <div style="color: #3498db; font-weight: bold; margin: 8px 0;">42mm</div>
                        <div style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9em;">85%</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: #ecf0f1; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
                        <div style="font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 8px;">બુધ</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 1.5em;">⛈️</div>
                        <div style="color: #3498db; font-weight: bold; margin: 8px 0;">58mm</div>
                        <div style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9em;">95%</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: #ecf0f1; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
                        <div style="font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 8px;">ગુરુ</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 1.5em;">🌧️</div>
                        <div style="color: #3498db; font-weight: bold; margin: 8px 0;">35mm</div>
                        <div style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9em;">75%</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: #ecf0f1; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
                        <div style="font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 8px;">શુક્ર</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 1.5em;">☁️</div>
                        <div style="color: #3498db; font-weight: bold; margin: 8px 0;">18mm</div>
                        <div style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9em;">45%</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: #ecf0f1; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
                        <div style="font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 8px;">શનિ</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 1.5em;">☀️</div>
                        <div style="color: #3498db; font-weight: bold; margin: 8px 0;">8mm</div>
                        <div style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9em;">25%</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: #ecf0f1; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
                        <div style="font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 8px;">રવિ</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 1.5em;">☀️</div>
                        <div style="color: #3498db; font-weight: bold; margin: 8px 0;">0mm</div>
                        <div style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9em;">5%</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ALERTS -->
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div style="background: #fff3cd; border: 2px solid #ffc107; border-radius: 10px; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;">
                    <strong style="color: #ff6b00;">⚠️ ભારે વરસાદ અલર્ટ</strong>
                    <p style="color: #666; margin-top: 8px; font-size: 0.95em;">બુધવાર 58mm વરસાદ અપેક્ષિત છે</p>
                </div>
                <div style="background: #d4edda; border: 2px solid #28a745; border-radius: 10px; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #27ae60;">
                    <strong style="color: #155724;">✓ વાવણી માટે આદર્શ</strong>
                    <p style="color: #666; margin-top: 8px; font-size: 0.95em;">જમીનમાં પૂરતો ભેજ છે</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- DISTRICT-WISE MONSOON DATA -->
            <div style="background: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: 2px solid #ecf0f1;">
                <h3 style="color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db; padding-bottom: 10px;">🌧️ જિલ્લા-વાર મોન્સુન ડેટા</h3>
                <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.95em;">
                    <thead>
                        <tr style="background: #ecf0f1;">
                            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 2px solid #bdc3c7;">જિલ્લો</th>
                            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #bdc3c7;">આ વર્ષે (mm)</th>
                            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #bdc3c7;">Normal (mm)</th>
                            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #bdc3c7;">તફાવત %</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ecf0f1;">સુરત</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #ecf0f1;">847</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #ecf0f1;">734</td>
